Hello,

I am Launching my First Dictionary Application Using MVC...

To make it work on your system clone it using github, Make sure u have the Java SE Platform and Eclipse and any Database Server.

Before Running application, run the following sql in the database manager(I used hsqldb, if u are on same then download it from hsqldb site
then go to bin->runserver->run manager in window select HSQL DataBase Engine Server in the drop down menu of type then click on ok)

create table registration(slno int generated by default as identity(start with 1,increment by 1) not null,name varchar(100) not null,email varchar(100) not null,primary key(slno));

create table users(slno int generated by default as identity(start with 1,increment by 1) not null,email varchar(100) not null,pass varchar(100) not null,reg_slno int not null,primary key(slno),foreign key(reg_slno) references registration(slno));

create table dict_name(slno int generated by default as identity(start with 1,increment by 1) not null,dname varchar(100) not null,dic_user_slno int not null,primary key(slno)),foreign key(dic_user_slno) references users(slno));


create table words(slno int generated by default as identity(start with 1,increment by 1) not null,text varchar(100),dict_slno int not null,primary key(slno),foreign key(dict_slno) references dict_name(slno));


create table pos_master(slno int generated by default as identity(start with 1,increment by 1) not null,pos varchar(30));


create table words_details(slno int generated by default as identity(start with 1,increment by 1) not null,meaning varchar(100) not null,example varchar(100) not null, word_slno int not null,pos_slno int not null,primary key(slno),foreign key(word_slno) references words(slno));

Just copy paste one by one, Then import it to eclipse by going File->import->General->FileSystem->Next->(To which Directory u had cloned) then select checkbox in eclipse->Finish.

So here we finishes the set up of the project.

Simply right click on project name in the project explorer of eclipse->runas->run on server(Make sure u had attached server to eclipse).